                        <interp inst="t18350302-name-577" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES PILLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a constable. I received it from Clark, and gave it to Stephenson.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350302-name-578" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350302-name-578" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
