                        <interp inst="t18350302-name-578" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN STEPHENSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I received the shilling from Pilley, and produce it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350302-name-579" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350302-name-579" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350302-name-579" type="surname" value="FIELD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350302-name-579" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. These are both counterfeit, but not from the same die.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never knew it was a bad shilling—directly she told me it was bad, I offered to give her another—I never was in the shop before.</p>
